# ❌⭕ Unbeatable Tic-Tac-Toe AI

A Python implementation using MiniMax algorithm that never loses!

## How to Play
```bash
python tictactoe.py
Enter numbers 0-8 to make moves:

Copy
 0 | 1 | 2
-----------
 3 | 4 | 5
-----------
 6 | 7 | 8
Features
Perfect AI using MiniMax

Simple 30-line implementation

Clear board display

MiniMax Algorithm
Simulates all possible moves

Scores outcomes (+1 win, 0 draw, -1 lose)

Chooses optimal move recursively

Try to beat it! (Spoiler: You can't 😉)

Copy

### 🚀 Run It!
1. Save as `tictactoe.py`
2. Run:
```bash
python tictactoe.py